long_description: The Swiss Army Tinker/Classic knife set pairs 2 of the most popular Swiss Army knives. The Tinker features 2 cutting blades, bottle opener with standard screwdriver, wire stripper, tweezers and toothpick. Also includes a can opener with small standard screwdriver, reamer with sewing eye, phillips screwdriver and key/lanyard ring. The Swiss Army Classic knife offers a bevy of functional tools in a pocket size. Stainless-steel components are strong and long-lasting. Rugged handles resist acids and solvents. Includes scissors and a sharp blade. Also includes a screwdriver, nail file, tweezers and toothpick. Crafted by Victorinox of Switzerland, these knives feature rugged stainless-steel components, sturdy handles and aluminum interior housings that ensure they'll last for years.
